1
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:26,990
[Brocade Odyssey]

2
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,810
[Episode 8]

3
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,000
It is only right to apologize

4
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,360
when you are at fault.

5
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:44,400
You don't have to dwell on it, Mr. Yang.

6
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:47,280
I lived in Yizhou for over ten years.

7
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,760
I am used to it.

8
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:52,200
Mr. Yang, if you truly regret your actions,

9
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,000
you should treat the Ji family

10
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,960
more favorably moving forward.

11
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,560
I'd better hurry back to dye the silk.

12
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,400
Wait a minute.

13
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,600
Since I'm here to apologize,

14
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,240
I must show some sincerity.

15
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,560
What is this?

16
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,160
There is nothing on it.

17
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,920
What is this?

18
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,320
A gift from you?

19
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,120
What kind of dye did you use?

20
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,520
How could you tell I used dye?

21
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,960
Well, I wouldn't be bothered

22
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,120
if you showed me something else.

23
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,760
So, do you want a favor,

24
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,480
or do you want this instead?

25
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,080
Why are you

26
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,560
so insincere?

27
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,520
If you're going to apologize, then do it properly!

28
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,560
Why are you making her choose?

29
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,600
You're right, Linglong.

30
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,600
Let's hurry.

31
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:17,800
Yingying said this is the first order for Bloom Society.

32
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,800
We need to make sure it gets delivered on time!

33
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:41,840
Mr. Jiang,

34
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,520
your wife

35
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,280
just called you home for dinner.

36
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,680
Alas, don't rush me!

37
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,240
Good work takes time!

38
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,920
It's time for some flower cookies.

39
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,640
Ms. Ji,

40
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,960
my madam requested to meet you.

41
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,440
Your madam is...?

42
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,840
The daughter of General Niu,

43
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,960
Ms. Niu.

44
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,960
I've never had any dealings with your madam.

45
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:21,160
Why would she want to meet me?

46
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,200
My madam saw the velvet flowers

47
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,360
you presented at the Splendor Showcase,

48
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,320
and she adored them.

49
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,760
She is asking

50
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,440
if you could replicate them

51
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,560
using the flowers she grows.

52
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:33,360
Can you... accept the order?

53
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,360
Well...

54
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:39,000
I'll have to take a look at the flowers first.

55
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,320
After them!

56
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,160
Yes, sir!

57
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:37,920
What happened?

58
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,800
As per your orders,

59
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,960
we had been scouting the cave for days.

60
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,400
Nothing happened at all.

61
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,000
But a group of people suddenly showed up

62
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,960
today and ambushed us.

63
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:50,960
[The Niu Residence]

64
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,400
Ms. Niu,

65
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,360
Ms. Ji has arrived.

66
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,040
Greetings, Ms. Niu.

67
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,160
Ms. Ji,

68
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,800
it's good to see you again.

69
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,320
Please, sit.

70
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,880
I've actually

71
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:36,160
wanted to meet you for a long time.

72
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,400
I'm merely a commoner

73
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:40,520
who happened to cross paths with you once.

74
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,720
How did you come to know of me?

75
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:46,200
Falling flowers filled the sky during the Splendor Showcase,

76
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,920
and Flushed Rose stunned the whole crowd.

77
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,240
Who in Yizhou

78
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,800
hasn't heard of you?

79
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:01,520
Actually, Ms. Ji, I admire you greatly.

80
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,920
You admire me?

81
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,360
Ms. Niu, you come from a distinguished background.

82
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,160
What's there to envy about me?

83
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,960
Ms. Ji, I want to be like you.

84
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,960
I want to build a career as a woman

85
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,600
and prove to my father that

86
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,720
a woman's future

87
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,640
is not only limited

88
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,000
to marriage.

89
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,360
Ms. Niu, you certainly are ambitious.

90
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,160
I'm sure you will achieve whatever you set your heart on.

91
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,600
What a fine tea.

92
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,360
Ms. Ji,

93
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,200
would you be interested in joining me

94
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,800
to oversee the brocade business in Yizhou?

95
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,520
I know that

96
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:01,400
you and Mr. Zhao are in love,

97
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,760
but the Zhao family opposes it.

98
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,640
I can help you

99
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,960
secure your marriage with him...

100
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,760
And restore the Ji family's prestige

101
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:16,760
from your father's era.

102
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,000
Ms. Niu,

103
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,160
with all your wealth

104
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,400
and influence,

105
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,560
why would you lower yourself

106
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:45,120
to pursue a career?

107
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,760
Merchants are considered the lowest of society.

108
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,960
Ms. Niu,

109
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,520
I truly find it hard to believe your words.

110
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,760
Ms. Ji, you're a very cautious person.

111
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,520
Very well.

112
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,240
Let me show you

113
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,360
why I want this.

114
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,080
This is...?

115
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,480
My mother.

116
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,680
My mother was only 16 when she married into this family

117
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,320
and bore five children for my father.

118
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,360
However, my father only desired a son

119
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,600
who could fight alongside him.

120
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,200
Sadly,

121
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,720
after five attempts,

122
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,160
all he had were daughters.

123
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,880
When I was born, my mother's health deteriorated,

124
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,840
and she could no longer bear children.

125
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:50,200
She never left the house ever since.

126
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,840
General,

127
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,440
when will you return?

128
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,120
Mrs. Niu...

129
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,080
She doesn't recognize me either.

130
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,320
General...

131
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,440
Now, she has become a woman

132
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:06,480
who only spends her days waiting for her husband's return.

133
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,240
My father

134
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,680
married off all four of my sisters

135
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,880
to men who could help him gain more power.

136
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,240
I, too, have been married twice,

137
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,680
but I won't accept my fate.

138
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,280
Since women can't be officials,

139
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,800
I'll venture into business.

140
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,360
I'll show my father that

141
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,280
I'm better than

142
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,840
any man he chooses for me.

143
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,400
Ms. Niu, you sure are ambitious.

144
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,520
I truly admire you.

145
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,680
Bloom Society

146
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:42,880
and Flushed Rose

147
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,200
have proved your worth.

148
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,120
Join me,

149
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,720
and you can reach even greater heights.

150
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,800
Together, we can take full control

151
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,480
of Yizhou's brocade business.

152
00:10:57,520 --> 00:10:59,760
Ms. Niu, you drive a tempting offer,

153
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,440
and I appreciate your honesty.

154
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,720
However, I believe that

155
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:07,040
personal feelings should never be mixed with business.

156
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,960
My feelings for Mr. Zhao

157
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,800
cannot be used as a bargaining chip.

158
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:13,200
Besides, I founded Bloom Society

159
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,320
to give people like Ms. Zhu and myself,

160
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,760
who have no status or power,

161
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,040
a way forward.

162
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,960
If I were to join forces with you,

163
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,640
I would be no different

164
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,800
from Mrs. Hua.

165
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,200
For that reason,

166
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,160
I must decline your offer.

167
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,920
As I have said,

168
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,280
Ms. Ji,

169
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,040
you still don't grasp

170
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,920
what it is like to hold true power.

171
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:40,440
True power

172
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,560
is the ability to prevent you from succeeding in anything

173
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,840
that goes against my will.

174
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:54,050
[Flushed Rose]

175
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,060
[Ji Yingying from Yizhou's Sandaoyan dyehouse created a new color, Flushed Rose]

176
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:00,520
[is approved for sale by the officer of the Weaving and Dyeing Bureau.]

177
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,560
Isn't this registration document

178
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:03,240
should be on its way to Chang'an?

179
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:05,960
No wonder

180
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,520
Mrs. Hua insisted

181
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:09,360
I take on the Flushed Rose orders that day.

182
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,440
Turns out there was more to it than I thought.

183
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:13,600
Ms. Niu,

184
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,560
you must be the rumored benefactor behind the Hua family.

185
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,000
That doesn’t matter.

186
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,200
The real question is,

187
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,400
will you

188
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,520
reconsider your decision?

189
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,560
I have made up my mind.

190
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:32,160
Thank you for your kindness, Ms. Niu.

191
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,360
It’s getting late. I'll take my leave now.

192
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:42,920
Ms. Ji, please wait.

193
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:45,600
What are you doing? Let go!

194
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,640
Let go of me!

195
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,560
Ms. Ji,

196
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,160
I gave you a chance.

197
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:14,160
Ms. Niu, your actions right now

198
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:16,000
only prove that I was right to reject your offer.

199
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,320
If you refuse to work with me,

200
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:20,160
then you'll serve me instead.

201
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:24,360
Ms. Ji, you can only leave this place

202
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,560
once you've dyed the Shu Red Silk.

203
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,200
Hold on.

204
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:39,200
It's too late

205
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,760
for regrets.

206
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,600
Ms. Niu,

207
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:46,160
can I send a letter to my family to let them know I'm safe?

208
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,200
I don't want to worry them.

209
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,120
Besides, I'm sure you don't want this to escalate either.

210
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,160
I may come from a humble background,

211
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:55,800
but Mr. Sang

212
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,520
is part of our Bloom Society.

213
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:02,960
Get her a pen and a paper.

214
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:04,360
Yes, madam.

215
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,440
Ms. Niu,

216
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:21,760
she is done.

217
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,520
Yaoting, Mother,

218
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,640
I have learned that

219
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:32,360
a landslide has happened 300 li outside Yizhou

220
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,600
and delayed the delivery of the registration document.

221
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:36,040
I have rented a carriage

222
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,200
to retrieve the document.

223
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,400
Time is tight.

224
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,960
I can't explain in detail.

225
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,960
Please forgive me.

226
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,600
Yaoting, Mother,

227
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,640
remember to buy more ingredients for the flower cookies and the rest.

228
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,520
We need a lot to produce Flushed Red.

229
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,240
I didn't have enough money

230
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,760
when I bought the dye last time.

231
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,800
Thankfully, Ms. Yu lent me two guan.

232
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:55,560
Please repay her for me.

233
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,040
Yaoting, Mother,

234
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,440
don't worry about me.

235
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,520
Deliver this to the Ji residence later.

236
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,520
Yes.

237
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:10,760
Keep an eye on her.

238
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,040
If she escapes, you'll pay for it with your life.

239
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,240
Understood.

240
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:26,800
These are all materials for dyeing Shu Red Silk.

241
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:29,120
Why are they all here?

242
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,280
Why aren't you working?

243
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:35,240
Stop dawdling!

244
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,440
I'm watching you.

245
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,720
These ordinary ingredients won't do

246
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,320
if you want to dye

247
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,440
Shu Red Silk.

248
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:44,200
Then what else do you need?

249
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:47,200
I need eight liang of ashes burned from redwoods,

250
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:50,160
one jin of madder from the rocks,

251
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:53,360
and three and a half jin of safflowers filled with morning dew.

252
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,200
That should be all.

253
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,800
Don't think of playing tricks.

254
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,320
Hurry and get them prepared.

255
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,560
Can you shoulder the blame

256
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,560
if there's a delay in the dyeing process?

257
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:07,360
You!

258
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,240
Wait here.

259
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,040
Ms. Niu,

260
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:35,320
can Ji Yingying really dye Shu Red Silk?

261
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:39,000
If she can dye it, we'll use hers.

262
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,280
If not, we'll use our own.

263
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,640
Mrs. Hua is already ruined,

264
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:44,960
and Ji Yingying refuses to comply.

265
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:47,840
Plus, the mountains are unsafe lately.

266
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,320
Even if it's not Yang Jinglan,

267
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:52,240
someone else

268
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,320
is surely targeting us.

269
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,400
The best way

270
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,680
to hide a drop of water

271
00:17:00,680 --> 00:17:02,160
is to place it in the sea.

272
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,360
A loom doesn't belong in the mountains,

273
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,400
but if it's placed in a brocade workshop,

274
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,720
no one will suspect a thing.

275
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:19,160
Ms. Niu,

276
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,360
there is a letter from the General.

277
00:17:25,120 --> 00:17:26,200
You may leave.

278
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:27,360
Yes, Ms. Niu.

279
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,040
Ms. Niu.

280
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:33,360
Read it.

281
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,200
Summarize the important parts for me.

282
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:36,800
Okay.

283
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:45,160
