00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,920
It's a distant relative of the Right Military Commissioner.

287
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:57,360
He wishes to take you as his concubine.

288
00:17:58,040 --> 00:17:58,760
General...

289
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:01,600
You're his daughter,

290
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:02,800
not a gift to be given away!

291
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,920
Quiet down.

292
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,360
This is the Niu residence,

293
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,320
not my home.

294
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,960
I just feel sorry for you, Ms. Niu.

295
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:17,760
The gentleman Ji Yingying fancies is from the Zhao family,

296
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:21,040
the renowned brocade merchants in Yizhou.

297
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:22,680
The name is

298
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,200
Zhao Xiuyuan, I believe?

299
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:25,760
I think so.

300
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:27,640
The Zhao family

301
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:29,800
is the perfect sea to hide the drop of water.

302
00:18:35,740 --> 00:18:45,430
[San Hua Pavilion]

303
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:03,320
This might be a mistake.

304
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:04,320
Please pardon me.

305
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:05,560
You are at the right place.

306
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:07,880
I was the one who invited you, Mr. Zhao.

307
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,920
And you are?

308
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:20,640
My father is Niu Jin, Vice Governor of Yizhou.

309
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:22,200
I am the fifth daughter in my family.

310
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:24,240
Surely you've heard of me.

311
00:19:26,080 --> 00:19:26,960
Ms. Niu,

312
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:30,040
why did you invite me here?

313
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:32,680
Do you intend to keep standing there

314
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,400
to speak with me?

315
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,000
We're strangers.

316
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,240
For the sake of your honor,

317
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:39,440
it's best that I remain standing here.

318
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:42,440
Surely you know about my reputation.

319
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,000
Staying there

320
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,440
isn't good for yours.

321
00:19:49,120 --> 00:19:50,520
If there's nothing else,

322
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,440
I'll take my leave.

323
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,240
I'm a friend of Ms. Ji.

324
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:56,840
She asked me to deliver a message to you.

325
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,200
Yu Yuan.

326
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,080
Yes.

327
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:08,040
Mr. Zhao, please wait a moment.

328
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,800
Ms. Niu,

329
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,680
what business do you have with me?

330
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,880
When people

331
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,000
see my face

332
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,840
and learn about my status,

333
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:52,280
they either fear me,

334
00:20:52,840 --> 00:20:54,720
avoid me, or fawn over me.

335
00:20:55,080 --> 00:20:55,840
But you're

336
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,600
the only one

337
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:58,800
who remains unmoved.

338
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,080
Are you

339
00:21:02,040 --> 00:21:03,040
not afraid of me?

340
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,240
I don't judge people by their appearances,

341
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:06,720
only by their hearts.

342
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,440
Excuse me.

343
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,720
Don't you want to hear

344
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,440
the message Ms. Ji left for you?

345
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:15,280
No.

346
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:18,960
Yingying would never entrust someone like you

347
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,040
to deliver a message to me.

348
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,560
What kind of person am I

349
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:23,080
in your eyes?

350
00:21:24,040 --> 00:21:24,920
Calculative

351
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:26,480
and unpredictable.

352
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,160
Alright.

353
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:32,520
Let me

354
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:33,840
bare my heart to you today.

355
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:39,000
I fell in love with you

356
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,480
at first sight.

357
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,760
I wish for you to accept me.

358
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:44,440
Careful with what you say.

359
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:46,440
I am already engaged.

360
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:49,400
I'm afraid I cannot reciprocate your affections.

361
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:52,280
Is it Ms. Ji from Huanhua Dyehouse?

362
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,000
Please don't come any closer.

363
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:58,360
But I have heard that

364
00:21:58,360 --> 00:22:00,120
the Zhao family has already annulled the engagement.

365
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:03,080
Even so, I only wish to marry Yingying in this life.

366
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:06,320
Please don't make it difficult for me.

367
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,840
Mr. Zhao,

368
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:11,440
do you realize the weight of my words?

369
00:22:12,520 --> 00:22:14,080
I am the daughter of Niu Jin.

370
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:16,440
There is nothing

371
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:18,520
I cannot achieve in Yizhou.

372
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,440
Everyone knows the power of General Niu.

373
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:23,680
But I truly seek nothing.

374
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,240
If there's nothing else today,

375
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:27,000
then

376
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,520
thank you for the hospitality.

377
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,440
I'll take my leave.

378
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:55,040
Ms. Niu, Mr. Zhao Sr. will soon hear about you

379
00:22:55,040 --> 00:22:56,640
reserving the entire San Hua Pavilion

380
00:22:56,840 --> 00:22:58,240
just to meet Mr. Zhao.

381
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:01,000
But will the Zhao family

382
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:02,840
really take action?

383
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:06,080
Mr. Zhao Sr. is a wise man.

384
00:23:06,520 --> 00:23:07,520
He will understand.

385
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:08,960
But Ms. Niu,

386
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:10,880
is Mr. Zhao really the one you want to choose?

387
00:23:20,360 --> 00:23:21,680
You think he is unsuitable?

388
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,480
He remained unfazed even after

389
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,520
learning about my identity.

390
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,680
He showed neither shock nor disdain

391
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:30,720
upon seeing my face.

392
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:32,440
Just for that alone,

393
00:23:32,560 --> 00:23:33,680
he stands above the rest.

394
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,760
But his heart already belongs to Ji Yingying.

395
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:37,880
He will never truly love you.

396
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:38,880
Love?

397
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:41,760
Do you think I need something like that?

398
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,800
Rather than letting my father marry me off

399
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:47,360
to some random household,

400
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:49,720
I'd rather act first.

401
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:53,800
The Zhao family is one I can control,

402
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:55,560
and one I urgently need to control.

403
00:23:57,320 --> 00:23:58,520
The Zhao family

404
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:00,920
is the perfect place to hide that drop of water.

405
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:03,240
With the Zhao family's brocade workshop,

406
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,480
I won't need to exhaust myself weaving brocade in the mountains.

407
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,480
Ji Yingying,

408
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:15,040
since you won't submit to me,

409
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,640
I will just take what you hold dear.

410
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,960
I wonder if Yaoting has received my letter.

411
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:40,680
I asked Ms. Yu about it.

412
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:41,760
She said dyeing Shu Red Silk

413
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:43,680
doesn't require the things you mentioned.

414
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,040
Are you playing me as a fool?

415
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:46,080
I'm the one dyeing the silk.

416
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:47,120
What would she know?

417
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:48,200
How dare you talk back?

418
00:24:48,760 --> 00:24:49,800
I'm going to teach you a lesson!

419
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:51,160
Let me teach you a lesson!

420
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:51,640
You!

421
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:52,520
Still running?

422
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:54,480
How dare you talk back?

423
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:55,960
Let's see where you can run.

424
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,520
You!

425
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:13,320
Why aren't you running?

426
00:25:14,560 --> 00:25:15,480
I'm telling you.

427
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,880
This is just a warning.

428
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:20,000
If you dare mess with me again,

429
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:21,680
you won't live to regret it.

430
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:25,800
Keep an eye on her.

431
00:25:42,410 --> 00:25:45,920
[The Zhao Residence]

432
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:46,720
Grandfather.

433
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:50,640
I heard

434
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:55,120
Ms. Niu has taken a liking to you.

435
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,560
Grandfather, you must be mistaken.

436
00:25:58,280 --> 00:25:59,720
I only met her briefly

437
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,560
by chance.

438
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,320
How could there be any interest?

439
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:04,280
Is it her disinterest

440
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,440
or yours?

441
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:16,120
You slighted Ms. Niu today.

442
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:17,400
Did you consider

443
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:21,920
if she bears a grudge,

444
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:25,720
Zhao Brocade won't stand a chance

445
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:28,040
against the Brocade Master?

446
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:33,920
Grandfather,

447
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:37,760
Yingying and I are in love.

448
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:38,760
I cannot accept

449
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:40,160
Ms. Niu's favor.

450
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,040
Foolish boy!

451
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:44,000
I approved your marriage with Ji Yingying

452
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,560
because of Bloom Society

453
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:47,840
and Flushed Rose.

454
00:26:48,360 --> 00:26:50,360
Your union with her will help our family greatly.

455
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,520
Xiuyuan,

456
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:56,200
but if you marry Ms. Niu…

457
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,320
I won't.

458
00:26:59,840 --> 00:27:00,680
How dare you!

459
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:05,520
A messenger has been sent to the Niu residence to propose marriage.

460
00:27:22,760 --> 00:27:23,800
Ridiculous!

461
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,200
Grandfather,

462
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:32,720
she wouldn't want to marry a cripple.

463
00:27:33,320 --> 00:27:34,360
My heart

464
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,440
will not change.

465
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,840
Then you'll kneel here

466
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:39,840
until you have thought it through.

467
00:27:40,080 --> 00:27:40,800
I will kneel.

468
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:42,760
I...

469
00:27:43,040 --> 00:27:43,600
Mr. Zhao Senior!

470
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:47,360
Here's a message from the Niu residence.

471
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:49,520
They are inviting Mr. Zhao to visit.

472
00:27:53,080 --> 00:27:54,880
Tell Ms. Niu that

473
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:58,520
Mr. Zhao will be there.

474
00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,080
Yes, sir.

475
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:17,500
[The Niu Residence]

476
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:31,400
You look rather worn, Mr. Zhao.

477
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,160
All thanks to you, Ms. Niu.

478
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,920
I have done nothing at all.

479
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:43,680
It was the Zhao family who came to my family seeking a marriage proposal.

480
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,920
The Niu family wields tremendous power.

481
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:49,040
We met at San Hua Pavilion yesterday.

482
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:50,920
Did you

483
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:52,840
plan all of this in advance?

484
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,360
Please.

485
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:32,880
Even if you dislike the idea,

486
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,440
you do not show it.

487
00:29:35,080 --> 00:29:36,440
Your composure is admirable, Mr. Zhao.

488
00:29:38,080 --> 00:29:39,160
Earlier,

489
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:40,760
you asked me if this was intentional.

490
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:43,200
I pity my sincerity.

491
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:45,520
You speak of it so disdainfully.

492
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,640
Let's be candid.

493
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:50,440
You are willing to lower yourself

494
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,800
to marry me, the son of a merchant.

495
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:54,920
What is your true intention?

496
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,680
Once we are married,

497
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,200
there are certain things

498
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:03,040
I will share with you.

499
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:04,680
Who would have thought

500
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:08,280
you are so desperate

501
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:10,040
to marry yourself off, Ms. Niu?

502
00:30:10,280 --> 00:30:11,080
How dare you!

503
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:18,120
Do you know

504
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:21,440
how I got this scar on my face?

505
00:30:26,430 --> 00:30:28,550
Everyone says I am cursed,

506
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:30,000
a bringer of bad luck to my husbands.

507
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:32,400
But in truth,

508
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:35,240
I wanted them dead.

509
00:30:36,080 --> 00:30:37,520
And so, they died.

510
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:42,240
This scar was my father's lesson to me.

511
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,240
He was furious at the time,

512
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:46,200
and his hand slipped.

513
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:49,120
But I am grateful for this scar.

514
00:30:50,520 --> 00:30:52,040
It earned me the opportunity

515
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:54,040
to hold power and make decisions.

516
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:58,440
Power once forced its will upon you.

517
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:01,440
Now you use it to force your will on others.

518
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:06,840
That is the beauty of power.

519
00:31:10,530 --> 00:31:13,590
[Yuebuhuan]

520
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,480
Yuniang?

521
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:20,680
Yuniang!

522
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:22,200
Are you looking for me?

523
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:24,200
It is Yingying who sent me.

524
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,160
She said when she bought dye the last time,

525
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,240
she borrowed two guan

526
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:28,040
but forgot to repay you.

527
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:28,920
I...

528
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:30,880
I have only managed to earn one guan.

529
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,520
Two guan?

530
00:31:34,840 --> 00:31:36,320
If I am ever in trouble,

531
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:38,440
I will send you a signal, Yu.

532
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,400
If I say,

533
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,680
I will repay one guan,

534
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,640
come and save me.

535
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:43,440
If I say, I will repay two guan,

536
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,480
bring Mr. Yang with you.

537
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:47,440
When did she ask you to come here?

538
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:48,320
Yesterday.

539
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:49,880
Why did you not come yesterday?

540
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:50,520
I...

541
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,440
I was busy collecting the money.

542
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,000
Where is she?

543
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:58,200
The letter said she went to investigate the registration document.

544
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,160
A letter?

545
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,920
You have not seen her in person?

546
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,080
Where is the letter?

547
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:04,800
The letter?

548
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:10,240
What had happened, Ms. Yu?

549
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,040
Wait for me outside.

550
00:32:14,820 --> 00:32:17,590
[From Yingying]

551
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:22,040
Why should I save you?

552
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,840
Mr. Yang, you love the people like they are your children.

553
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:26,800
I do not acknowledge a rebellious child like you.

554
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:29,320
If I am in such dire trouble

555
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:30,920
that I need both of you to save me,

556
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:34,080
then anything you wanted to know before,

557
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,040
you may ask,

558
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,080
and I will answer.

559
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:38,440
Even if I want to save you,

560
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:40,040
I need to know where you are.

561
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:41,640
We have this.

562
00:33:01,280 --> 00:33:02,640
What exactly happened?

563
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:04,880
Nothing. You should go home.

564
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:06,680
But Yingying only left a letter and disappeared.

565
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,840
I am worried about her.

566
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:08,240
Maybe

567
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,880
I should hire a carriage and go find her.

568
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:10,720
I will go find her.

569
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,640
You stay home and wait.

570
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:13,640
No, I will go.

571
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,600
Go home and wait! Trust me.

572
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:27,320
I invited you here today

573
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,920
to enjoy a play

574
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:30,280
with me.

575
00:33:31,600 --> 00:33:32,520
Perhaps after watching,

576
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:35,040
you will reconsider your decisions.

577
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:43,000
Ms. Niu said

578
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,200
to give you half an hour to escape.

579
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:49,080
What kind of new torment is this?

580
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:51,080
It is a chance to live.

581
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:53,040
It all depends on whether you want it or not.

582
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:19,360
Yingying!

583
00:34:33,640 --> 00:34:34,800
What are you trying to do?

584
00:34:35,240 --> 00:34:36,680
Just inviting you to watch a play.

585
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:40,200
Best stay away from the windows, Mr. Zhao.

586
00:34:40,680 --> 00:34:43,240
These archers cannot hear sudden noises.

587
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:47,120
Otherwise, they might shoot at Ms. Ji.

588
00:34:59,240 --> 00:34:59,720
Ms. Niu!

589
00:34:59,720 --> 00:35:00,200
Do not move!

590
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:02,600
Do you believe I will kill you?

591
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,440
A cornered beast fights hardest.

592
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,840
Do you not find it entertaining?

593
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:15,960
Ms. Ji,

594
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,520
your time is running out.

595
00:35:17,520 --> 00:35:18,640
Will you continue?

596
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,320
I really will kill you!

597
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:48,120
Can you face the consequences

598
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:49,920
after killing me?

599
00:35:50,920 --> 00:35:52,760
Can the Ji and Zhao families

600
00:35:53,560 --> 00:35:54,840
bear the consequences?

601
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:10,280
I am sorry.

602
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:11,040
I will release you

603
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:11,840
once I am outside.

604
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,480
Let me go...!

605
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:17,720
Do you hear that?

606
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:18,880
Release her!

607
00:36:20,640 --> 00:36:22,600
What a match made in heaven.

608
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:24,840
Even your escape plans

609
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,640
are identical.

610
00:36:27,640 --> 00:36:28,440
Let me go!

611
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:17,280
Are you insane?

612
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:23,080
Mr. Zhao, you clearly have never killled anyone.

613
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,040
Do you want to kill me?

614
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:27,480
Should I have them

615
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:29,280
kill a few more

616
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,840
to teach you how it is done?

617
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:50,440
What exactly are you trying to do?

618
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:58,440
I have already told you.

619
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:00,840
From the moment I saw you,

620
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,040
I was captivated.

621
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:04,040
I wish for us to get married.

622
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,920
I hope you will grant my wish.

623
00:38:07,990 --> 00:38:10,370
[Marriage Agreement]

624
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,200
Will you release Yingying

625
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,240
if I agree to this?

626
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,400
That depends on

627
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,080
whether you are willing

628
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:38,800
to treat me sincerely in the future, Mr. Zhao.

629
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:01,760
How insolent!

630
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:03,000
You dare cause trouble at the Niu residence!

631
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:06,840
Hand Yingying over immediately!

632
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,040
Ms. Niu,

633
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:11,320
there is an urgent decree from the palace.

634
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,760
They want Shu Red Silk.

635
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,120
I have already reported to the governor.

636
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:16,680
I must take Ji Yingying, the daughter of the Red Silk Brocade Master,

637
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:18,240
to assist with the investigation.

638
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,400
Ms. Niu,

639
00:39:21,240 --> 00:39:22,400
surrender her at once.

640
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:27,040
Mr. Yang, you are quite the strategist.

641
00:39:27,240 --> 00:39:28,640
You are not to be underestimated.

642
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:31,960
But I think you misunderstand, Mr. Yang.

643
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,520
Ms. Ji did visit my residence,

644
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,320
but she has since departed.

645
00:39:37,240 --> 00:39:38,800
Whether she is here or not,

646
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,000
I will know after I search.

647
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:42,560
The General's residence

648
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:45,320
is not a place you can search at will.

649
00:39:45,760 --> 00:39:46,760
The emperor's order cannot be defied.

650
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,360
Ms. Niu,

651
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:50,840
do you intend to resist an imperial decree?

652
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:00,960
If you fail to find her,

653
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:04,040
