654
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:06,360
will not be easily excused.

655
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:07,560
Fine.

656
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:10,160
Forgive the intrusion.

657
00:40:11,560 --> 00:40:12,440
Search everywhere!

658
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:12,960
Yes, sir!

659
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:55,080
Mr. Yang, no sign of her on the eastern side.

660
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:01,840
Mr. Yang,

661
00:41:03,720 --> 00:41:04,720
