662
00:41:05,160 --> 00:41:05,960
Keep searching!

663
00:41:06,160 --> 00:41:06,960
Yes, sir.

664
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:56,800
How dare you act on your own?

665
00:41:58,320 --> 00:41:59,320
Did I not instruct you

666
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:01,160
to escort Ms. Ji safely back to her house?

667
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:03,360
How could you do something so foolish?

668
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:04,200
Please forgive me, miss.

669
00:42:04,560 --> 00:42:06,520
I saw Ms. Ji behaving arrogantly and rudely,

670
00:42:06,640 --> 00:42:08,160
and I felt indignant.

671
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:10,280
That is why, in a moment of folly, I made such a grave mistake.

672
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,920
Please spare me, miss.

673
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:14,720
Do you realize

674
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:16,360
if today's event were to spread,

675
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,600
and Ms. Ji's reputation were ruined,

676
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:18,760
even death would not atone for your actions?

677
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:20,960
Enough, Ms. Niu.

678
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,920
This act of pity has gone far enough.

679
00:42:27,120 --> 00:42:27,800
I will not

680
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:28,960
